{"title":"山岭的回响——一个老兵的旅游记","authors":["李冰"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":8,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岭的回响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一个老兵的旅游记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李冰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从梦里走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数十年行程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扑进你坦荡的胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这起伏的崇山峻岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这风啊，是山岭伸出的手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象母亲的手抚摸着我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这般粗砺，这般有力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这风啊，是山岭在呼吸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同母亲的话语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一洗我身上的污泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这风啊，象母亲递来的清水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝一口，我又毅然站起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那温柔的暖风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往往使人昏迷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这山岭的劲风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人陡然清醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还给我丢失的智力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这赭红的岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千姿百态，成群结队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同雕像林立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长，你在哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时候，你说过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是一块岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和这山岭不可分离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刹那间，整个连队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成燃烧的岩浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋葬了顽敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这块突兀的岩石可是你？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英姿如许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棱角分明，怒目而立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当清早"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那晨露为你解渴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当傍晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你招来晚霞——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起连队那面战旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长，你在时刻注视，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这前沿阵地，那茫茫天际。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在辨别，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是枪声，还是花炮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是硝烟，还是炊烟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，你随时准备出击。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几道闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥起战刀猛劈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊雷四起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震得天宇欲坠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍山岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛要拔地飞起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岭啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你胸中储存的炮火迸放？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天弹药纷飞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊雷啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你在高声呼喊？注意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，是的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不敢沉睡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也未敢麻痹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安逸并非幸运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震荡给生命以活力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮声乃出击的前奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声是使人惊醒的乐曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我梦见我已经死去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和连队不曾分离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我梦见我已经死去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成一缕炽热的飞灰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那片青云，是我的军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那颗星星，是我的帽徽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我飞遍山岭阵地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯视祖国山水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莽莽千山万岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披云戴霞撑天而立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前辈英烈，同辈战友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见你们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和这山岭凝结一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化成大地的骨骼——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臂膀和脊椎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国山岭才如此雄伟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岭啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你吞食过多少硝烟？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾吐出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是这洁白的云雾缕缕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你咽下多少血泪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷放出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是这乳汁样的净水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山岭啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你保存着我的青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你火热的心地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你需要的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让山风唤我返回。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}